description:
Sanzo, Goku, Gojyo and Hakkai are back, but this time they might be in over their heads! After rescuing the beautiful Houran from a demons attack, the four are invited to her masters sprawling mansion for some rest and relaxation... a visit that may cost them their lives. Little do they know that the master is up to no good, and has cleverly ensnared them in a game of life and death that involves shikigami, dopplegangers, betrayals and a plot for revenge that threatens to consume them all!

